- `cache_all`: Caches all requests.

- `bypass_all`: Bypasses the cache for all requests.', example='cache_all'),
  cacheDeceptionArmor?: string(name='CacheDeceptionArmor', description='Specifies whether to enable cache deception defense. This feature helps defend against web cache deception attacks. When this feature is enabled, only content that passes validation is cached. Valid values:

- `on`: Enables the defense.

- `off`: Disables the defense.', example='on'),
